race.comment: SILENT ASSASSIN (7) missed the frame last time at this track but just three runs back rocketed around 520m at this track in 29.65. Has the ability and expected to go close again. PANADERO MAGIC (1) turned in a plain run last time when seventh at this track over 520m behind Aston Walker (31.16) in a Grade 4/5. Was a winner prior to that. Boasts a strong record from this draw with two wins and two minor placings from five starts. Warrants plenty of respect. BORACAY SUMMER (6) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (29.93) at this track. Has a strong winning record here at this journey. Expected to be in the finish again. ANOTHER JAMES (8) is a last-start placegetter worth considering.
